node.text:
With Leah Wyer SVP/GM of @byrdie and Founder/ Partner  of @sblabeauty, @randishinder, and me.
I promised I would put up our #instagramlive conversation but as It was a stormy day we lost our connection ( and probably a lot of you 😉) several times so I will post the snippets we were able to salvage . And @sandylinter this one includes a shout out to legendary you. So in case you were #wand-ering …here’s a bit about #sblawands and what the silver neck chin and jawline #wand can do for you! And thank you again @leahwyar for gracing us with your presence you are pure delight! #selfcaresunday 💜💛

node.text:
With an Attitude of gratitude and @sblabeauty ‘s peptides and actives like Hyaluronic Acid Complex which delivers lipids which replenish moisture, plumps skin cells, reduces lines and wrinkles and visibly tightens the skin.
And Our SBLA Proprietary Double Peptide Blend which increases collagen production, reduces lines & wrinkles, and increases skin firmness.
Skin Repair & Brightening Blend containing Acetyl Glucosamine (Amino Acid) to moisturize, brighten & even out skin tone, repairs & treats sun damage ( hello!) while reducing age spots. 🙌🏼I’ll drink to that! Cheers! 
It also reduces puffiness & inflammation as well as tightens and firms loose skin.

See I told you, things are looking up! 
Hope you enjoyed this video which are condensed excerpts from my conversation with @breannenyc during our zoom with @womenatmeredith Thank you I loved chatting with you! 💕

“Everybody’s Talking About Jamie” is the name of the 
F A B U L O U S 🎉FILM
Hosted by superstar supercharming hostess of this screening of this  MUST SEE JOYOUS FILM @janekrakowski_sunshine we were reminiscing about being in @nationallampoonsvacation movie together (she stole the show as usual) Anyway… 
Everyone WILL be talking about this sweet smart delightful film that will fill your heart with glittery joy and LOVE ‼️Shantay Sashay your way to this film‼️
PS The last video is how this film made me feel💃❤️💜💙💚💛🧡 #latergram from Friday night

node.text:
It took a French Hurricane named Henri to keep our show @celeb_autobio from going on …believe me we’re all as disappointed as you probably are but we are in the bullseye of a significant storm that’s threatening to knock out power and down trees so with your safety and the safety of the cast in mind, the decision was made to cancel the show. 
I hope the Producers are able to reschedule the show so we can share some laughter together real soon!
 #soldout #hurricainehenri  #cancelled #showcancelled #changeofplans #thatsshowbiz

node.text:
Hello my fellow Nature Lovers and Gardeners🌺 By now I’m sure you’ve all read about the devastating UN Report on Climate Change …and being the beautiful souls that you are, you’re now all looking for ways to help our beautiful Mother Earth and all her sentient beings …so I just want to remind you of the power of growing your own slice of earth organically… from your lawn to your  flowers and vegetable garden please avoid pesticides and herbicides that thru run off are polluting our rivers oceans and bodies. And killing off our pollinators the Bees so crucial to keeping our food supply productive. 
It’s easier than you think, and you’ll become part of the solution rather than contributing to the problems. Swipe thru to see a few shots from my organic garden for proof that you don’t need the chemicals! 🌼🪴🌻🐿
#organic #garden #organicgardening #gardeningtips  #climatechange #togetherwecan 🌱🌱🌱
